itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:11:36.000Z","msg":"咁呢堆人原本應該乜柒都唔會幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66c787b53a00706f3cbc1b7d1e5ff65327503b2","tid":1213374,"uid":15677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:12:20.000Z","msg":"真心撐嘅話如何可以變唔撐<br />\n唔撐個啲證明佢地短視 叫佢地檢討下自己先"},{"pid":"ebe468bf8fdd8198beebdffeae7d89cb8ce39eed","tid":1213374,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:12:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母 本身覺得琴日係暴動既人點撚都憎架啦 講到要呢班on9有用咁"},{"pid":"45d4ede9a32ab3bfd36e051b1471f7801e2cfffb","tid":1213374,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"只要你反對你就係搞事，要撐既點都會撐，要反你你唔出聲都係反你"},{"pid":"6edafddc514ea235187cf8e8d288ff47a969b783","tid":1213374,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"289b298b1659742098f15514e099f0b0e47e5cbe","tid":1213374,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:27:38.000Z","msg":"攪立會好過啦<br />\n攪地鐵把咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:18:14.000Z","msg":"真係唔好，始終社會里豬多，你殺佢可以，你唔比野食佢就會開始咬人"},{"pid":"4110f162baf7fa014cee666cbb2ab6d9b409cdc6","tid":1213374,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2162d28840f227cda3061e554bf6e932124c9119","tid":1213374,"uid":22362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:23:50.000Z","msg":"你講個可行既方案出黎<br />\n你依家去到金鐘咩<br />\n人地沿途已經部署晒啦傻仔<br />\n琴日冇部署都可以趕晒走<br />\n今天埋到去既機會係零<br />\n除非真係有一堆勇士敢玩火<br />\n不過以我對香港人既認識係冇<br />\n塞地鐵先係低成本高效益<br />\n長期持久戰"},{"pid":"b62de701aec1027de3c2e3eee89020aab45cf4c5","tid":1213374,"uid":84040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"其實係咪天真到覺得搞唔到佢地就冇野?<br />\n問下你身邊上一代<br />\n去下藍絲page到睇<br />\n有幾多個係當班義士係為香港<br />\n喺佢地眼中係暴民係外國勢力搧動係收左錢咋<br />\n<br />\n和理非<br />\n你睇下薯片佬，你問下d 7,80後<br />\n個撚個都話唔好去唔好搞咁多野<br />\n呢d事係犯法又危險<br />\n有邊個當你義士咁拜<br />\n<br />\n支持既自然會支持<br />\n唔支持既繼續唔支持<br />\n<br />\n你覺得霸金鐘中環就唔會搞到佢?"},{"pid":"5780b013a8ee8a5cd79fdb0d158f608a933ddbcc","tid":1213374,"uid":183781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"次次有咩都話和平理性<br />\n睇下仲有幾多次和平理性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩唔好俾機會狗察老解<br />\n講到好似得香港有軍/警咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩完一晚<br />\n今日二讀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抗爭/革命 有邊次唔流血"},{"pid":"a8a59922b2cdf718240c889849cd2a400e6cbfbb","tid":1213374,"uid":41130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a9948389d4fbb8857d81b14980a12c1023602c1","tid":1213374,"uid":51920,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:35:43.000Z","msg":"屌 今日覆唔到疹 排多次要二年後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:32:28.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦，你係steam 呃左咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70aeffaacdf097e55fed979a29614e77131ae8bf","tid":1213374,"uid":20916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"民意未必make it better<br />\n但絕對可以make it worse<br />\n呢次好明顯溫和派（簡單D講就係民意）都好包容勇武派，士氣先咁高漲<br />\n所以所有行動最好睇睇風向"},{"pid":"38d2fb0845ec60d0ce466c4a423e8fa8db6f7f67","tid":1213374,"uid":43304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"306412a93f01e5cf57b5d1624b950252b1d8386a","tid":1213374,"uid":238551,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"631139d6a4550fab69bd58ddece19eb16f531be2","tid":1213374,"uid":34571,"like":200,"dislike":7,"score":193,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"覺得你玩野 ， 唔知你為咩， 民意又逆轉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:59:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"5年前鳩嗚玩膠果啲咪柒過一次囉<br />\n點解會學唔精, 唔吸收教訓..白白失敗<br />\n有心係好. 但無腦唔掂喎"},{"pid":"95aacff75624f5f09b13683ef11ec64bf780d472","tid":1213374,"uid":226126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-1